title: ssh: Example is not standalone
body:
The SSH Dial example at
http://godoc.org/code.google.com/p/go.crypto/ssh#example-Dial
has a snippet ClientAuthPassword(password("yourpassword"))
in it, but does not define type password.

The implementation is actually in
https://code.google.com/p/go/source/browse/ssh/client_auth_test.go?repo=crypto#92

The example would be better if it actually worked as a full example.
